ISLAMABAD, Jan 23 (APP):Prime Minister Imran Khan Sunday expressed concern about President of Maldives Ibrahim Mohamed Solih who tested COVID positive.
In a tweet on social media platform Twitter, he said, “Concerned to hear that the President of Maldives Ibrahim Mohamed Solih tested Covid positive. My prayers for your speedy recovery & good health.”
